{"tid":2252956,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"凶宅陷阱｜新手爸誤租謀殺案雙屍單位 質疑經紀淡化凶情","createTime":"2020-10-21T23:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T14:58:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1002d7c9c19a7c20afea6d0cfe32ce6ee603c960","tid":2252956,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:56:24.000Z","msg":"疫情下本港經濟日差，樓價卻持續高企、繼續是一屋難求。有地產經紀及業主疑為促成交易而出「茅招」，令市民在半知情甚至不知情的情況下誤租或誤買凶宅，苦不堪言。《蘋果》發現，有新手爸爸為改善生活環境「膽粗粗」租住凶宅，承租後才赫然發現租用的單位原來並非只是涉及多年前普通自殺案，而是去年一宗逆女弒母案的凶案現場，疑遭地產代理誤導，對方卻矢口否認，令投訴變羅生門；另有男租客在不知情下租住了曾發生「王嘉梅碎屍慘案」的劏房凶宅後，同住女友屢遇離奇的疑似靈異事件，最終不堪精神壓力要搬走，直至記者採訪時男事主才驚悉原來自己一直居於凶宅，對業主不誠實的推銷手法，難禁怒火中燒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201022/SKQDVFBMTBAJVNXO235YHJGBUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201022%2FSKQDVFBMTBAJVNXO235YHJGBUE%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPWSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=2302c0fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201022%2FSKQDVFBMTBAJVNXO235YHJGBUE%2F&h=011d936e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201022/SKQDVFBMTBAJVNXO235YHJGBUE/</a>"},{"pid":"74559b7da45f7e676b1591f2925b71d8cfd1383c","tid":2252956,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:58:25.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩 自己嚇自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有撚咁多靈異野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79139766cd114c1222d4956104b248efcdf5230b","tid":2252956,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:59:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NwFMQyFlXP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNwFMQyFlXP4&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPWSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=b715700a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NwFMQyFlXP4</a>"},{"pid":"7b132c8386bb87329a1c6348eb9ba4088d36b07c","tid":225